{"tid":272943,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【名家搶先睇】David Webb復仇記（周顯）","createTime":"2017-06-06T07:42:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-07T05:52:14.000Z","uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a432674f7d3a1ac4ab05981d3412adb2c6db4859","tid":272943,"uid":17738,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T07:42:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170606/large/1496730785_28a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170606%2Flarge%2F1496730785_28a0.jpg&h=8e7b21b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周一晚，證監會發出指令：「符合投資大眾或公眾之利益」，將隆成金融（1225）停牌，因為2015年的供股通函包括了重大失實、不完整或錯誤引導資料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n幾年前，David Webb持有一隻股票，被莊家收購了。莊家馬上供股，Webb竟然跟供，有一天，我踫到了該位莊家，他很有風度地說：「佢咁叻，咪畀佢贏錢囉。」據悉，這一役，Webb贏了三千萬元，揚長而去。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n然後，隆成金融被另一位仁兄收購了，據說，有人善意向他作出勸誡：「喂，David Webb有份，不如講數，至少給他全身而退吖。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可惜這位仁兄的習慣是從來無數講：「呸，使鬼同他談判，供死佢咪得囉。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結果，2015年供股，Webb（也許是食髓知味）竟然跟供，在2016年再供一次，Webb終於投降，沽貨打靶，據說輸了幾千萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一年多後，Webb公佈了「不能買的50隻股票」，中心點就是隆成金融（1225），其中的二十多隻是同一網絡，明顯就是以此為打擊重心。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這份名單的廣為傳播，實則上已打擊了整個網絡的資金鏈，周一證監會的行動，究竟是不是由Webb提供研究資料，便不得而知了。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這故事的教訓是一，千萬別因小失大。二，更不要得罪權勢人士。<br />\n<br />\n周顯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56790602&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56790602%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&d=KAzopUd0ERei3WjkYpC2T5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=9e362386\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56790602%26category_guid%3D7015342%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170606&h=99079477\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56790602&amp;category_guid=7015342&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170606</a>"},{"pid":"400cfe2b37af58179b0a88645581384b2b922a8f","tid":272943,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:51:21.000Z","msg":"等啲老千股玩得咁開心，成日供股合股耍供再合，長期唔賺錢只係吸啲小股民嘅血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係為全部股東搵錢嘅公司留係到上市做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4caac8168d4ec6b698b5ffe30709c361a1ea3812","tid":272943,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T08:58:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>等啲老千股玩得咁開心，成日供股合股耍供再合，長期唔賺錢只係吸啲小股民嘅血<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔係為全部股東搵錢嘅公司留係到上市做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n香港真係污煙瘴氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c96550f3f4fc0726b3e139b1766e926a95ab19","tid":272943,"uid":997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"見財化水 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d617617f50aa9681ebb99b6b7d84e3b44a81838","tid":272943,"uid":66157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T10:05:11.000Z","msg":"原來Webb仲有隆成股份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】隆成金融表示，證監會有意勒令股份於今早9時起停牌，但股份仍錄得七宗成交，至9時30分才被證監勒令停牌，港交所表示，有關成交有效。<br />\n<br />\n兩年內三度供股，原名隆成集團的隆成金融周一深夜發通告，指接獲證監函件，有意根據證券及期貨規則第8(1)條勒令股份，於今早9時停牌，不過，在競價時段已錄得一宗成交，開市後5秒內，再錄得六宗成交才停牌，停牌前報0.127元，大跌9%，涉資12.6萬元。<br />\n<br />\n港交所回應指，證監於今早9時30分才勒令隆成停牌。<br />\n<br />\n隆成的通告指，證監認為集團於2015年，一份有關供股的通函有重大失實、不完整或錯誤引導資料，當時已大力批評公司折讓近70%供股，大幅攤薄股東持股的David Webb指，或跟當時供股後，股東架構出問題有關，證監應盡快採取法律行動。<br />\n<br />\n隆成透過這次供股，將公眾持股量由逾80%大幅降至20%，連同往後一年合股再供股，已被市場人士質疑大玩財技，變相更換大股東，隆成最近試圖第三度供股，並將股份1拆50，集資4.6億元。<br />\n<br />\n本身持有隆成股份，但上月將其納入「50隻不宜沾手港股名單」的David Webb認為，集團坐擁4億元現金，無需要再供股，重申公司股權複雜，證監應該調查。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=223778\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223778&d=KAzopUd0ERei3WjkYpC2T5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=f643f0c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Ffinance%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D223778&h=0cd7c161\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/finance/player?newsId=223778</a>"},{"pid":"f71bd4377e8f75f7889ffb18640da10c64042a0d","tid":272943,"uid":43587,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-06T15:19:37.000Z","msg":"第一隻係咩股咩莊"},{"pid":"5330e154447f812d128069c996d679d4817e9467","tid":272943,"uid":31907,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-07T05:52:14.000Z","msg":"周顯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}